short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension is here to get your ID from TCHUB to be able to get your summit rank on discord using TheCrewExchange's bot.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension is here to generate for you the command that you need to send if you want to be able to get your summit stats directly on discord. Just send the command generated by the addon to TheCrew-Exchange#4900 and you account will be linked !
After that just use the command "!tce ss" to get your stats.
